Making Your YouTube Embeds Mobile Responsive with Bootstrap
https://www.solodev.com/blog/web-design/making-your-youtube-embeds-mobile-responsive-with-bootstrap.stml

<!-- 16:9 aspect ratio -->
<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
  <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="..." allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div>

The standard aspect ratio for YouTube on a computer is 16:9. - from https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/6375112

<!-- 21:9 aspect ratio -->
<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-21by9">

<!-- 4:3 aspect ratio -->
<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3">

<!-- 1:1 aspect ratio -->
<div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-1by1">



